name: hades style sorta
description:
this was trained on the character portraits of Megaera, Nyx, Hades, and Zagreus. pretty bad faces on SD1.5 but other models pretty much fix it.

trained for like 3000 steps on 424x424 images, switched to closeups of their faces for a few hundred to try to get the faces better, but idk.

modelVersions.name: V1
modelVersions.description: first one, pretty good I think but idk. first image was SD1.5 with a bunch of my other embeddings, first three images after that were generated with genericfemalemix2.1, the two anime ones after that are anything3, and the rest are SD1.5
